加護病房醫療團隊包括：<ref>{{Cite web|title=高雄榮總重症加護|url=https://org.vghks.gov.tw/icu/4.html|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504091531/https://org.vghks.gov.tw/icu/4.html|archive-date=2020-05-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
